{"tid":1151084,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖〉教煮 水煮手撕蔥蝦仁蛋花湯","createTime":"2019-05-12T10:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T06:21:07.000Z","uid":97125,"like":4,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"cc826c38e335afa9e258d87068fbbde3c3067224","tid":1151084,"uid":97125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"1. 主要食材<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GL4XwuQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGL4XwuQ.jpg&h=b4821b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSipVWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSipVWu.jpg&h=2acba179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 用黎水煮嘅水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2skf2Ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2skf2Ca.jpg&h=6ec17d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 加手撕蔥，可以連刀都唔使用 ( 適合 兒童做)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ghpgM4r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FghpgM4r.jpg&h=4317116e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 落蝦先因為難熟過蛋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D9bnHC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD9bnHC7.jpg&h=aef646ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.放蛋，半生熟都食得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ky9P65m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKy9P65m.jpg&h=ddc51d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6. 完成！！ 可以唔使放鹽因為啲蝦本身鹹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a2YxkqM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2YxkqM.jpg&h=ba3daee5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d894303a264b894cfa13466dfbec532cd35d442","tid":1151084,"uid":38904,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"廚餘湯?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\"